      "solution": "#include <iostream>\nusing namespace std;\n\nint reverseNumber(int n) {\n    int rev = 0;\n    while (n > 0) {\n        rev = rev * 10 + (n % 10);\n        n /= 10;\n    }\n    return rev;\n}\n\nint main() {\n    int N;\n    cin >> N;\n    cout << (N + reverseNumber(N)) << endl;\n}\n",
